WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 13=

01:43.990 --> 01:45.550
(Liang)
(Duan Xu ambushed)

01:45.860 --> 01:47.700
(Luozhou)
(the enemy in Luozhou,)

01:47.910 --> 01:48.750
(using the terrain.)

01:49.300 --> 01:50.500
(The elite Chong forces)

01:50.750 --> 01:52.300
(held the Capital and Youzhou)

01:52.470 --> 01:53.343
(and refused to help.)

01:53.690 --> 01:54.976
(Luozhou)
(Luozhou was retaken.)

01:55.580 --> 01:56.420
(Two months later,)

01:56.750 --> 01:59.020
(Yunzhou)
(Yunzhou was also retaken.)

01:59.020 --> 01:59.990
(Luozhou)

01:59.990 --> 02:03.060
(North Chong was still mired
in the succession struggle,)

02:03.390 --> 02:04.580
(unable to act.)

02:04.750 --> 02:06.470
(For nearly half a year, Liang's war)

02:06.670 --> 02:08.350
(Liang)
(shifted from defense to attack)

02:08.670 --> 02:10.900
(and finally paused for a time.)

02:15.020 --> 02:15.860
Meng.

02:17.460 --> 02:18.300
Where is the General?

02:18.860 --> 02:20.270
He said he'd return to Nandu.

02:20.740 --> 02:21.853
So, he won't travel with us.

02:24.020 --> 02:25.650
Meng, let us go now.

02:25.860 --> 02:27.420
The General and Xiaoxiao

02:27.420 --> 02:28.580
will take care of themselves.

02:30.616 --> 02:31.745
The General is going to meet

02:31.756 --> 02:32.430
some friends.

02:32.550 --> 02:33.583
We'll meet again in Nandu.

02:35.140 --> 02:35.980
In that case,

02:36.180 --> 02:37.070
once we reach Nandu,

02:37.390 --> 02:38.550
I'll drink

02:38.730 --> 02:39.783
with some old friends too.

02:40.400 --> 02:41.420
Thanks for the invitation.

02:41.580 --> 02:42.620
I will be there on time.

02:44.550 --> 02:45.830
As for your drinking capacity,

02:47.110 --> 02:48.300
you should sit with Chenying.

02:49.223 --> 02:50.956
- I can't drink.
- Compared with last time,

02:50.967 --> 02:51.950
I can do much better now.

02:53.350 --> 02:54.670
Then I shall look forward to it.

02:59.340 --> 03:01.380
(Liang)

03:11.830 --> 03:12.670
Simu.

03:16.990 --> 03:17.830
Eat it.

03:24.180 --> 03:25.600
Aren't you going to ask what it is?

03:27.270 --> 03:28.110
You wouldn't harm me.

03:29.510 --> 03:30.350
If you meant me harm,

03:30.633 --> 03:31.826
there'd be nothing I could do.

03:36.110 --> 03:36.950
What you swallowed

03:37.270 --> 03:38.740
was the Spirits Lantern in sugar.

03:40.900 --> 03:41.740
The Spirits Lantern?

03:41.751 --> 03:43.017
An artifact of the Spirit World.

03:43.300 --> 03:44.670
With it, one's spirit power

03:44.670 --> 03:45.670
can grow over tenfold.

03:46.140 --> 03:47.460
It represents the Sovereign.

03:47.950 --> 03:49.700
All spirits crave it deeply,

03:49.830 --> 03:51.390
each desperate to claim it first.

03:51.740 --> 03:53.180
And now it's inside you.

04:22.790 --> 04:23.670
Simu,

04:26.500 --> 04:27.693
this is what a spirit is like.

04:46.380 --> 04:47.260
Foxy,

04:48.990 --> 04:50.820
welcome to the world of spirits.

05:20.710 --> 05:21.550
From now on,

05:22.110 --> 05:23.670
you can use Deliverance's power

05:23.990 --> 05:25.180
to awaken the Spirits Lantern.

05:29.180 --> 05:30.566
You feared that after the exchange,

05:30.666 --> 05:32.239
you'd be a mortal
without spirit power,

05:32.500 --> 05:33.380
so you

05:33.380 --> 05:34.670
made me a spirit to protect you.

05:35.500 --> 05:36.350
I suppose so.

05:37.790 --> 05:38.630
Surely,

05:39.150 --> 05:39.990
I won't fail you.

06:05.940 --> 06:06.780
What are you doing?

06:20.180 --> 06:22.406
Jade-like petals wet with dew
release a fragrant bloom.

06:22.740 --> 06:24.500
Before spring, they await their prime.

06:25.710 --> 06:28.460
Their scent leaves the soul spellbound.

06:32.620 --> 06:34.350
A fragrant breeze
enthralls the passerby.

06:36.076 --> 06:37.445
So, the things in my father's book

06:37.456 --> 06:38.020
were all true.

06:41.350 --> 06:42.190
Simu,

06:44.740 --> 06:46.260
welcome back to the human world.

06:50.670 --> 06:54.380
♪Falling down like snow♪

06:54.850 --> 06:58.330
♪Joys and sorrows of the mortal world♪

06:58.330 --> 07:02.210
♪Swept along by the daylight♪

07:02.620 --> 07:06.420
♪The forms and hues of the mortal realm♪

07:06.690 --> 07:09.360
♪Lingering for a fleeting moment♪

07:09.520 --> 07:13.840
♪Was once touched by laughing tears♪

07:14.320 --> 07:17.230
♪If I could live a simple life♪

07:17.230 --> 07:18.070
♪For once♪

07:18.070 --> 07:23.150
♪I'd be a guest in a sweet dream♪

07:25.240 --> 07:28.740
♪Dawn and dusk rise and set♪

07:29.010 --> 07:32.540
♪Longing to meet, yet parted by destiny♪

07:33.050 --> 07:36.660
♪Let me wander through♪

07:36.660 --> 07:40.300
♪Light and dark, without turning back♪

07:40.710 --> 07:44.110
♪Wander to the other shore
with the lantern♪

07:44.240 --> 07:48.240
♪Accompanied by eternity♪

07:48.450 --> 07:51.140
♪As all things turn and flow♪

07:51.260 --> 07:57.170
♪Whether I stay or go, I'm all alone♪

08:00.180 --> 08:01.020
Simu.

08:02.620 --> 08:03.460
Simu.

08:11.530 --> 08:14.900
♪Falling down like snow♪

08:17.110 --> 08:18.110
What is that scent?

08:21.420 --> 08:22.350
This is

08:24.790 --> 08:25.630
agarwood,

08:27.260 --> 08:28.100
amber,

08:30.350 --> 08:31.190
storax,

08:32.380 --> 08:33.230
mint leaves,

08:33.230 --> 08:34.070
Bletilla,

08:34.380 --> 08:35.220
and benzoin.

08:37.310 --> 08:38.336
My sister loves fragrance.

08:38.710 --> 08:39.550
She uses fragrance

08:40.500 --> 08:41.470
to scent

08:41.470 --> 08:42.310
my everyday robes.

08:43.620 --> 08:44.460
Agarwood,

08:46.020 --> 08:46.860
amber,

08:47.470 --> 08:48.350
storax,

08:49.380 --> 08:51.430
mint leaves, Bletilla,

08:52.380 --> 08:53.260
and benzoin.

08:55.360 --> 08:59.030
♪Light and dark, without turning back♪

08:59.230 --> 09:00.070
It smells wonderful.

09:00.070 --> 09:02.990
♪Wander to the other shore
with the lantern♪

09:03.060 --> 09:07.130
♪Accompanied by eternity♪

09:07.130 --> 09:09.710
♪As all things turn and flow♪

09:09.980 --> 09:13.140
♪Whether I stay or go, I'm all alone♪

09:13.190 --> 09:14.500
The army has returned to rest.

09:15.830 --> 09:16.950
I happen to be free as well.

09:17.990 --> 09:18.830
How about I travel

09:19.540 --> 09:20.540
with you for a while?

09:28.620 --> 09:29.710
Come with me to Youzhou

09:29.900 --> 09:31.190
to meet an old friend.

09:32.540 --> 09:33.540
I happen to know

09:33.540 --> 09:34.710
a gifted fragrance maker

09:35.710 --> 09:36.550
in Youzhou.

09:36.990 --> 09:37.830
Do you want to learn

09:38.140 --> 09:38.980
fragrance-making?

09:39.620 --> 09:40.660
If you do,

09:41.530 --> 09:42.380
start by blending

09:42.380 --> 09:43.220
the scent on me.

09:44.100 --> 09:44.950
Why must it be

09:44.950 --> 09:46.070
the scent on you?

09:46.070 --> 09:48.680
♪A lone lamp shines on the other shore♪

09:48.710 --> 09:50.190
Because you like it.

09:51.783 --> 09:52.670
How long will it take?

09:54.070 --> 09:54.910
Until the day

09:56.710 --> 09:58.070
our time is up.

10:00.020 --> 10:00.860
What if

10:01.430 --> 10:02.310
I fail by then?

10:04.656 --> 10:05.950
I haven't picked the stakes yet.

10:06.263 --> 10:07.220
You can owe me for now.

10:11.740 --> 10:12.990
Don't be so sure you'll win.

10:18.710 --> 10:20.190
Their mutton soup is excellent.

10:21.070 --> 10:21.990
You should have a bowl.

10:21.990 --> 10:23.020
Then I must try some.

10:31.140 --> 10:34.860
(Fujian City, Youzhou)

10:36.260 --> 10:37.100
Yili'er,

10:37.540 --> 10:38.990
there's still no progress

10:39.260 --> 10:40.190
on the royal order.

10:41.350 --> 10:42.260
Are you unwilling

10:42.260 --> 10:43.430
to serve the royals again?

10:45.540 --> 10:47.990
This concerns the war with Great Liang.

10:48.590 --> 10:49.860
The Royal Court needs you

10:49.860 --> 10:51.900
to find a new gold mine
for military pay.

10:52.420 --> 10:54.060
(Yili'er, Youzhou merchant)
In a week,

10:54.070 --> 10:54.910
we'll come again.

10:55.590 --> 10:56.609
I only hope that by then,

10:56.780 --> 10:57.760
you can give us

10:57.760 --> 10:58.830
a clear answer

10:59.230 --> 11:01.780
and ease the Royal Court's burden.

11:03.230 --> 11:04.070
Yes.

11:04.780 --> 11:07.260
I won't fail the Royal Court.

11:24.660 --> 11:28.380
(South Gate)

11:56.350 --> 11:57.380
My kid will love it.

11:57.380 --> 11:58.220
Youzhou has grown

11:59.190 --> 12:00.350
so prosperous.

12:01.430 --> 12:02.270
Tight defenses,

12:02.990 --> 12:03.830
full granaries.

12:05.140 --> 12:06.720
Luckily, we didn't attack Youzhou first.

12:09.180 --> 12:14.900
(Fragrance)

12:14.900 --> 12:15.830
Goodbye.

12:16.110 --> 12:17.140
Thank you.

12:19.190 --> 12:20.230
Miss, have a look around.

12:20.470 --> 12:22.070
We have fresh fragrance balls today.

12:25.900 --> 12:26.780
What a lovely scent.

12:27.350 --> 12:28.260
This is it.

12:29.310 --> 12:30.196
Let's choose this one.

12:35.710 --> 12:36.550
Miss,

12:36.830 --> 12:37.860
are you Liu Ruyu?

12:47.230 --> 12:48.830
Where did this sachet come from?

12:54.230 --> 12:55.190
Its owner said

12:55.540 --> 12:57.070
you'll understand after this letter.

13:01.580 --> 13:03.580
(To Liu Ruyu)

13:03.580 --> 13:05.180
(My friend is interested in fragrance.)

13:05.180 --> 13:06.715
(You're the expert. Please guide her.)

13:06.726 --> 13:07.700
(Duan Shunxi)

13:09.610 --> 13:10.470
Brat!

13:10.470 --> 13:11.500
Stop running if you dare!

13:15.020 --> 13:16.140
Stop!

13:21.540 --> 13:22.380
You...

13:29.310 --> 13:30.190
I just bought

13:30.190 --> 13:31.590
this pellet drum for you.

13:33.500 --> 13:34.470
Do you like it?

13:34.770 --> 13:35.620
I do.

13:35.620 --> 13:37.140
Thank you, Mother.

13:37.590 --> 13:38.900
Good girl.

13:39.230 --> 13:40.070
Mother,

13:40.260 --> 13:41.660
I'm hungry.

13:41.770 --> 13:42.620
All right.

13:42.620 --> 13:43.710
I'll go home and make

13:43.860 --> 13:44.700
some goodies for you.

13:45.070 --> 13:46.470
My power has grown far too much.

13:46.710 --> 13:47.620
I lost control.

13:50.190 --> 13:51.030
Who are you?

13:51.230 --> 13:52.350
Why slay a spirit here?

13:54.110 --> 13:54.950
My apologies.

13:55.230 --> 13:56.070
I didn't mean to.

14:01.350 --> 14:02.190
Forget it.

14:02.540 --> 14:04.110
It was a spirit marked for death.

14:04.590 --> 14:06.430
I'll just report what happened.

14:07.740 --> 14:08.580
Still,

14:08.780 --> 14:09.830
how did you manage

14:10.260 --> 14:11.110
with a spirit body

14:11.110 --> 14:12.350
to wield a mortal spirit sword?

14:14.780 --> 14:15.990
I've long since lost my memory.

14:16.790 --> 14:18.020
When I'm conscious,

14:18.660 --> 14:20.110
I've had this sword on me.

14:22.620 --> 14:23.460
You must've

14:23.620 --> 14:24.470
just become a spirit

14:24.620 --> 14:25.780
from Spirit Aura.

14:26.950 --> 14:28.350
No wonder you know so little.

14:30.020 --> 14:30.860
Young fellow,

14:31.590 --> 14:32.710
were you making an arrest?

14:34.190 --> 14:35.030
That's right.

14:35.310 --> 14:36.900
But don't call me young fellow.

14:37.243 --> 14:38.732
In the Spirit World, rank isn't judged

14:38.743 --> 14:39.310
by appearance.

14:39.310 --> 14:40.230
I'm over 600 years old.

14:41.710 --> 14:42.590
You look

14:43.350 --> 14:44.310
quite young.

14:44.590 --> 14:46.020
You ought to call me sir.

14:48.260 --> 14:49.100
I see.

14:49.470 --> 14:50.620
Please enlighten me, sir.

14:51.350 --> 14:52.860
You were seizing that spirit.

14:53.310 --> 14:54.403
What offense did he commit?

14:54.620 --> 14:55.660
Killing without cause

14:55.730 --> 14:56.936
in the 32 Golden-wall Decrees.

14:57.620 --> 14:58.700
That is a grave offense.

14:59.190 --> 15:00.830
I have hunted him for days by order.

15:02.260 --> 15:04.220
(Li Renyi)

15:05.710 --> 15:07.540
The 32 Golden-wall Decrees?

15:09.110 --> 15:10.190
Please tell me about them.

15:10.753 --> 15:11.942
Otherwise, I may break the law

15:11.953 --> 15:12.700
without knowing it.

15:13.540 --> 15:15.430
Your memory loss is thorough indeed.

15:16.780 --> 15:17.620
Fine then.

15:17.620 --> 15:18.500
You're pitiful.

15:18.500 --> 15:19.473
I'll explain as we walk.

15:19.893 --> 15:21.480
It was hard coming to the mortal world.

15:21.540 --> 15:22.900
I should enjoy myself.

15:27.020 --> 15:28.780
(Fragrance)

15:28.780 --> 15:29.620
I have remained here,

15:29.620 --> 15:31.190
awaiting news from Mr. Duan.

15:31.740 --> 15:32.590
Youzhou is now

15:32.590 --> 15:33.680
under North Chong's rule.

15:33.990 --> 15:35.350
You must be extra cautious.

15:36.540 --> 15:37.710
Please don't take offense.

15:40.710 --> 15:41.860
(Foxy)

15:41.860 --> 15:42.950
(has long placed)

15:42.950 --> 15:44.350
(his own eyes in Youzhou.)

15:44.740 --> 15:45.826
Mr. Duan said in his letter

15:46.140 --> 15:47.786
that you wish to learn
fragrance-making.

15:50.310 --> 15:51.740
But that's no easy craft.

15:53.140 --> 15:54.140
If you can name

15:54.140 --> 15:56.110
the aromatic ingredients
in this floral dew,

15:56.780 --> 15:58.140
then I can teach you.

16:06.380 --> 16:07.740
The ingredients for this floral dew

16:08.306 --> 16:09.655
can all be found on these shelves,

16:09.666 --> 16:10.220
right?

16:13.990 --> 16:15.020
Of course.

16:19.990 --> 16:21.500
Aren't you forbidden from coming here?

16:21.900 --> 16:23.780
Coming here unapproved also breaks

16:23.780 --> 16:24.900
the Golden-wall Decrees.

16:30.470 --> 16:32.020
Miss, look.

16:32.020 --> 16:32.860
Stop.

16:33.110 --> 16:33.950
You can't do that.

16:34.860 --> 16:36.350
If you take things directly,

16:36.500 --> 16:37.350
to mortal eyes,

16:37.350 --> 16:39.110
won't they just float in midair?

16:39.660 --> 16:40.740
Look carefully.

16:41.710 --> 16:43.020
When no one is looking,

16:43.500 --> 16:45.660
wrap the item with spirit power,

16:46.190 --> 16:47.590
make it unseen,

16:48.900 --> 16:50.070
and then pick it up.

16:53.190 --> 16:54.310
Let me take another look.

16:54.470 --> 16:55.310
Alright.

17:05.330 --> 17:06.170
Let's go.

17:07.580 --> 17:09.020
The 32 Golden-wall Decrees

17:09.230 --> 17:09.830
were agreed on

17:09.841 --> 17:11.350
by the former Sovereign and the Lords.

17:11.500 --> 17:13.100
But somehow,

17:13.100 --> 17:14.710
they were never carried out then.

17:14.880 --> 17:15.740
They were shelved.

17:15.740 --> 17:17.100
Once the current Sovereign

17:17.390 --> 17:18.430
took the throne,

17:18.630 --> 17:19.910
she revived the decrees.

17:20.060 --> 17:21.300
Any spirit that defies in secret

17:21.300 --> 17:23.100
or rejects the law is annihilated.

18:06.340 --> 18:07.450
You know nothing of spices,

18:07.575 --> 18:09.295
yet you picked out
the matching ingredients

18:09.306 --> 18:09.929
by scent alone.

18:10.500 --> 18:11.710
You truly are gifted.

18:13.670 --> 18:15.540
I owe it to him for lending me his nose.

18:16.390 --> 18:17.230
What did you say?

18:18.470 --> 18:19.310
Nothing.

18:19.670 --> 18:21.100
So, may we begin learning

18:21.100 --> 18:21.940
fragrance-making now?

18:27.060 --> 18:27.900
You make

18:28.292 --> 18:29.866
the current Sovereign sound impressive.

18:30.150 --> 18:30.990
Of course.

18:31.540 --> 18:33.100
Though these laws are restrictive,

18:33.300 --> 18:34.266
they do have some merit.

18:34.950 --> 18:36.020
Ever since she took charge

18:36.190 --> 18:37.223
and enforced the decrees,

18:37.260 --> 18:38.150
the Moral

18:38.150 --> 18:39.630
and Spirit Worlds knew peace.

18:40.836 --> 18:42.465
The evil spirits caught
by Starhaven Sect

18:42.476 --> 18:43.163
will be sent

18:43.174 --> 18:44.540
to the Spirit World for judgment.

18:44.540 --> 18:45.493
Each does their own job.

18:46.390 --> 18:47.260
It's no surprise.

18:47.260 --> 18:48.160
The Sovereign's mother

18:48.170 --> 18:49.390
was once a Starhaven sorcerer.

18:52.820 --> 18:53.660
Her mother

18:53.990 --> 18:55.230
was a Starhaven sorcerer.

18:56.780 --> 18:57.620
What?

19:00.580 --> 19:01.406
Have you ever seen

19:01.417 --> 19:02.340
the current Sovereign?

19:03.230 --> 19:04.500
I never have, actually.

19:05.190 --> 19:06.100
But I heard

19:06.630 --> 19:07.670
she's wrapped in malice,

19:07.950 --> 19:08.820
with bloodthirsty eyes

19:08.820 --> 19:09.710
and a ghostly face.

19:11.630 --> 19:12.780
Do not laugh.

19:12.780 --> 19:14.190
She's slain

19:14.190 --> 19:15.430
many Lords.

19:15.870 --> 19:17.340
She is even capable of wiping out

19:17.340 --> 19:18.340
all evil spirits.

19:19.060 --> 19:20.910
You came here without permission.

19:21.150 --> 19:22.260
If the Sovereign knows it,

19:22.630 --> 19:23.540
the Lord you serve

19:23.910 --> 19:24.870
will be in trouble.

19:25.100 --> 19:25.940
Perhaps

19:26.150 --> 19:27.430
you will be utterly annihilated.

19:38.150 --> 19:39.100
Today,

19:39.100 --> 19:40.820
our meeting must be fate.

19:41.990 --> 19:42.830
I won't breathe

19:42.840 --> 19:43.990
a word of your secret.

19:44.260 --> 19:45.430
Lend me your spirit sword

19:45.430 --> 19:46.270
for a few days, okay?

19:48.870 --> 19:49.796
This is a spirit sword.

19:49.837 --> 19:51.196
It didn't choose you as its master.

19:52.390 --> 19:53.230
You can't touch it.

19:54.060 --> 19:55.060
Why can you touch it?

19:55.187 --> 19:57.260
You got friendly
with a Spirit Official quite fast.

19:59.060 --> 20:01.150
Spirit Official? A mortal girl.

20:01.780 --> 20:02.670
In broad daylight,

20:02.670 --> 20:03.710
how did she spot us?

20:04.500 --> 20:05.540
How did your lessons go?

20:08.670 --> 20:09.510
Not very well.

20:09.990 --> 20:11.500
It's fine. We still have time.

20:11.500 --> 20:12.340
Master Yili'er.

20:12.670 --> 20:14.710
- Master.
- Master Yili'er.

20:14.710 --> 20:15.816
This is my family heirloom.

20:16.430 --> 20:17.540
Please take a look for me.

20:18.710 --> 20:19.580
Master.

20:19.580 --> 20:20.580
Master Yili'er.

20:21.260 --> 20:22.260
Master Yili'er.

20:23.580 --> 20:24.420
A treasure.

20:25.630 --> 20:26.950
Well, I have something to do.

20:26.950 --> 20:27.790
Bye.

20:28.340 --> 20:29.190
Please have a look.

20:29.190 --> 20:30.470
It's ancestral and very fine.

20:32.380 --> 20:33.940
(Grace Garden)
No entry.

20:34.870 --> 20:36.140
- Master.
- You can't enter.

20:45.470 --> 20:46.580
Everyone, go on back.

20:49.780 --> 20:51.020
Stop pushing.

20:51.340 --> 20:52.190
He can see me.

20:54.300 --> 20:55.300
It looks that way.

20:57.540 --> 20:59.190
Step back. Step back.

20:59.290 --> 21:00.150
Master Yili'er.

21:00.150 --> 21:01.100
Stop pushing.

21:01.100 --> 21:02.100
Master.

21:04.290 --> 21:05.150
Come back another day.

21:05.150 --> 21:06.020
What are you doing?

21:06.020 --> 21:07.230
Getting his attention.

21:07.970 --> 21:08.560
That man

21:08.571 --> 21:09.780
must be the most famous Yili'er

21:09.780 --> 21:10.630
in Youzhou.

21:16.230 --> 21:17.070
Let's go.

21:34.536 --> 21:35.670
So, this is what mortals call

21:35.670 --> 21:36.736
the bustle of mortal life.

21:38.190 --> 21:39.403
It really is a mix of scents.

21:39.910 --> 21:40.990
I can smell everything.

21:46.670 --> 21:48.190
Tell me about that Yili'er.

21:50.183 --> 21:52.036
It's rare for you
to be interested in mortals.

21:53.020 --> 21:53.860
This Yili'er branch

21:54.060 --> 21:55.630
is kin to the North Chong Royal Court,

21:56.060 --> 21:57.353
though the tie is a distant one.

21:57.500 --> 21:58.470
A fringe clan like this

21:58.470 --> 21:59.670
had little wealth to its name.

21:59.870 --> 22:00.990
But after coming to Youzhou,

22:01.740 --> 22:03.490
somehow their luck turned.

22:03.780 --> 22:04.870
They bought a hill

22:05.630 --> 22:06.580
and found a gold mine.

22:07.903 --> 22:08.820
Before long, he amassed

22:08.830 --> 22:09.809
a sizable family fortune.

22:09.820 --> 22:10.660
Even his son

22:10.660 --> 22:12.300
was promoted in the Capital.

22:13.343 --> 22:14.469
I heard Yili'er brought back

22:14.780 --> 22:16.230
quite a few treasures

22:16.390 --> 22:17.420
made for the Royal Court…

22:20.470 --> 22:21.310
Be careful.

22:22.470 --> 22:23.540
To his Treasure Vault

22:24.300 --> 22:25.540
in Youzhou.

22:29.230 --> 22:30.470
You just said

22:30.820 --> 22:31.950
the Treasure Vault?

22:33.670 --> 22:35.100
You want his riches too?

22:36.150 --> 22:36.990
It's hot.

22:57.710 --> 22:58.550
Why?

22:59.740 --> 23:00.740
It has been two months,

23:00.990 --> 23:02.470
and you still ignore me.

23:04.580 --> 23:06.430
Lord of Jiling Temple.

23:15.430 --> 23:16.270
I...

23:22.540 --> 23:23.380
Exactly.

23:25.870 --> 23:26.710
Treasures…

23:29.230 --> 23:30.100
The Treasure Fair

23:34.710 --> 23:37.260
will surely draw you out.

23:39.260 --> 23:40.580
I'll change the question.

23:41.300 --> 23:42.300
Why do you think

23:42.300 --> 23:43.140
he is so lucky?

23:43.540 --> 23:44.380
I heard

23:44.540 --> 23:46.230
some trade for luck, fame, and gain

23:46.430 --> 23:47.300
with spirits.

23:48.150 --> 23:49.020
Is Yili'er also

23:49.540 --> 23:50.540
dealing with spirits?

23:58.260 --> 23:59.540
One day, I must treasure

23:59.540 --> 24:00.780
your clever little skull.

24:04.950 --> 24:06.390
What a unique way to praise someone.

24:07.150 --> 24:08.150
Which one would you like?

24:08.340 --> 24:09.300
You may have a taste.

24:19.646 --> 24:21.100
Where did this copper coin come from?

24:21.100 --> 24:21.940
Dear, come look.

24:22.990 --> 24:23.830
What happened here?

24:24.390 --> 24:25.710
A copper coin just fell

24:26.710 --> 24:27.670
from nowhere.

24:28.870 --> 24:29.803
Where did it come from?

24:30.990 --> 24:31.910
What is going on here?

24:31.910 --> 24:32.750
No idea.

24:33.230 --> 24:34.670
Could that young lady have left it?

24:35.470 --> 24:36.310
Could it be?

24:37.060 --> 24:38.170
He got lucky

24:38.356 --> 24:39.909
because he struck a deal with a spirit.

24:40.470 --> 24:42.103
So, he'd offer a treasure
to that spirit.

24:43.540 --> 24:44.390
Could that bell

24:45.020 --> 24:46.060
be proof of the deal?

24:48.260 --> 24:49.795
When a mortal has a deal with a spirit,

24:49.806 --> 24:50.570
a token may be left

24:50.630 --> 24:51.580
for them to connect.

24:53.470 --> 24:54.870
Do you know who that spirit is?

24:56.780 --> 24:58.060
Our long-missing Lord

24:58.060 --> 24:58.910
of Jiling Temple,

24:59.060 --> 24:59.900
Song Xingyu.

25:01.470 --> 25:03.020
The Spirit Official you met today

25:03.020 --> 25:03.860
is a Jiling,

25:03.913 --> 25:04.990
also called a child spirit.

25:05.710 --> 25:06.670
They've become spirits

25:06.670 --> 25:07.556
for hundreds of years,

25:07.680 --> 25:08.540
but they still look

25:08.540 --> 25:09.910
like youths.

25:16.710 --> 25:17.692
Did that Spirit Official

25:17.703 --> 25:18.780
ask you for anything?

25:20.300 --> 25:21.340
He wanted my Deliverance.

25:24.669 --> 25:26.382
Most Jiling have
little worldly experience,

25:26.540 --> 25:27.430
so they desire

25:27.580 --> 25:28.710
everything in this world.

25:29.060 --> 25:30.100
They want everything

25:30.780 --> 25:32.470
but lose interest once they have it,

25:32.730 --> 25:33.580
forever chasing

25:33.580 --> 25:34.630
their next desire.

25:36.670 --> 25:37.630
So,

25:37.630 --> 25:38.870
they are the easiest to stir up,

25:38.870 --> 25:40.476
never learning, and are used by others.

25:41.930 --> 25:43.019
Is the Lord of Jiling Temple

25:43.030 --> 25:43.660
the same?

25:44.820 --> 25:45.660
He is even worse.

25:46.340 --> 25:47.950
When I put down the chaos,

25:48.190 --> 25:49.540
Song Xingyu fled the Spirit World

25:49.780 --> 25:50.630
with the Glazed Pagoda

25:50.780 --> 25:51.620
and the Lord Token.

25:52.190 --> 25:53.670
Two months ago, when I was attacked,

25:53.970 --> 25:54.820
I saw Song Xingyu's

25:54.820 --> 25:55.780
unique Puppet Technique.

25:55.780 --> 25:56.990
That is why I came here.

25:57.603 --> 25:58.818
To take back the Glazed Pagoda

25:58.829 --> 25:59.583
and the Lord Token?

26:11.300 --> 26:12.140
Your Grace,

26:12.967 --> 26:14.327
do you need shelter from the rain?

26:18.910 --> 26:20.190
I may have no sense of taste now,

26:20.630 --> 26:21.470
but I can smell.

26:22.720 --> 26:23.650
I've long wanted to try

26:23.650 --> 26:24.580
the scent of this brew.

26:24.580 --> 26:33.860
(Wine)

26:38.060 --> 26:38.900
It's raining.

26:48.260 --> 26:49.100
What is that smell?

26:50.150 --> 26:51.060
It's the smell of rain.

26:52.870 --> 26:54.230
Rain carries the scent of the sky

26:55.260 --> 26:56.493
and draws out the earth's scent

26:57.300 --> 26:58.950
and the vitality of all living things.

27:00.820 --> 27:01.670
So, Simu, look.

27:02.470 --> 27:03.630
Even if you can't sense it,

27:04.540 --> 27:06.100
you can still feel the weather.

27:20.740 --> 27:21.580
How wonderful.

27:25.230 --> 27:26.070
How wonderful.

27:40.150 --> 27:40.990
To tell scents apart,

27:41.300 --> 27:42.766
there must be enough scent particles.

27:43.490 --> 27:44.340
Moist air

27:44.340 --> 27:45.190
helps your nose

27:45.500 --> 27:46.500
catch scent particles.

27:48.020 --> 27:48.950
When flowers and grain

27:48.950 --> 27:49.790
are brewed into wine,

27:50.580 --> 27:52.820
their aroma gains a charm.

27:58.540 --> 27:59.380
This wine

27:59.710 --> 28:00.550
is called Nü'erhong.

28:01.150 --> 28:02.710
When a daughter is just born,

28:03.150 --> 28:04.383
her family takes glutinous rice

28:04.430 --> 28:05.760
to brew three jars and bury them

28:05.950 --> 28:07.150
beneath the osmanthus tree.

28:07.630 --> 28:09.150
When she marries at 18,

28:10.060 --> 28:11.080
they're considered a gift.

28:12.870 --> 28:14.060
It smells wonderful,

28:14.630 --> 28:16.430
but it tastes rather faint.

28:18.060 --> 28:18.950
This is grape wine.

28:19.340 --> 28:21.260
It's made from grapes and sugar.

28:21.260 --> 28:22.100
On the nose,

28:22.470 --> 28:23.580
it has a fresh grape aroma.

28:24.020 --> 28:24.860
And sweet rice wine.

28:25.150 --> 28:26.580
Its rice aroma is rich and sweet.

28:34.710 --> 28:35.550
Your Grace,

28:36.430 --> 28:37.390
you are a mortal now.

28:37.910 --> 28:38.950
You can't taste it,

28:39.540 --> 28:40.630
but you may still get drunk.

28:42.190 --> 28:43.260
What does that mean?

28:48.580 --> 28:49.820
You shouldn't drink more.

28:50.540 --> 28:51.500
I want to drink.

28:51.500 --> 28:52.540
How dare you stop me?

28:53.990 --> 28:54.653
I would not dare.

28:54.765 --> 28:55.941
Still, this is your first time

28:55.952 --> 28:56.972
drinking in a mortal body.

28:57.303 --> 28:58.504
You shouldn't drink too much.

29:00.950 --> 29:01.820
It's been 400 years.

29:03.190 --> 29:04.990
This is the first time
I've smelled wine.

29:05.470 --> 29:06.580
Yet, you're stopping me.

29:19.100 --> 29:19.940
Foxy,

29:20.670 --> 29:22.060
just let me have a taste.

29:47.780 --> 29:50.660
(Wine)

29:59.710 --> 30:00.550
Promise me.

30:01.936 --> 30:03.022
This will be your last pot.

30:05.950 --> 30:06.790
All right?

30:38.580 --> 30:39.420
You feel no touch.

30:39.950 --> 30:41.150
Isn't a bed wasted on you?

30:42.060 --> 30:43.500
You've got quite the nerve.

30:44.630 --> 30:46.630
Isn't it a shame you're a mortal?

31:04.390 --> 31:05.576
Your brows stretch like hills.

31:07.430 --> 31:08.630
Your waist sways like a willow.

31:09.680 --> 31:11.380
Freshly adorned,
you face the spring wind.

31:12.670 --> 31:13.876
One smile outshines a fortune.

31:15.710 --> 31:16.630
Your Grace,

31:20.710 --> 31:21.710
in your long life,

31:22.720 --> 31:23.775
you must've made many men

31:23.786 --> 31:24.540
fall for you.

31:39.280 --> 31:42.900
♪Spring comes; ice and snow thaw♪

31:44.760 --> 31:51.000
♪All things wake, with the east wind♪

31:53.850 --> 31:58.300
♪In the season at its fullest♪

31:59.340 --> 32:05.680
♪Light the lamps
to pierce the old night♪

32:10.150 --> 32:17.140
♪Borrow mortal warmth to ease the cold♪

32:17.620 --> 32:21.070
♪Warm winds bring fragrant blooms♪

32:21.580 --> 32:23.020
You made the first move.

32:24.670 --> 32:25.510
He Simu,

32:26.870 --> 32:28.230
if I wanted to kiss you now,

32:30.150 --> 32:31.060
would you say yes?

32:32.080 --> 32:40.990
♪With light, carefree words,
still shining bright♪

32:41.620 --> 32:44.800
♪A pot of wine in fleeting dreams♪

32:45.020 --> 32:46.950
Your eyes are beautiful.

32:48.820 --> 32:49.780
You want to keep them?

32:53.820 --> 32:56.020
Eyes are best when they're living.

32:57.780 --> 32:58.630
Is that so?

33:00.020 --> 33:01.580
Then you'd better keep me alive.

33:01.580 --> 33:04.600
♪Let me savor this fleeting joy♪

33:04.830 --> 33:11.860
♪May I roam drunk in dreams
and never forget♪

33:12.060 --> 33:19.080
♪Please ferry me once through this life♪

33:19.340 --> 33:29.050
♪In the netherworld, I see a ray♪

33:31.460 --> 33:34.170
♪To what home shall I return♪

34:42.500 --> 34:43.340
Who hit me?

34:44.060 --> 34:44.900
No one.

35:05.500 --> 35:06.340
Someone did.

35:08.350 --> 35:09.190
Who is there?

35:10.350 --> 35:11.190
Show yourself.

35:33.990 --> 35:34.830
What is that thing?

36:22.270 --> 36:23.830
Thank you, Your Grace, for saving me.

36:48.310 --> 36:49.150
This room is soiled.

36:49.580 --> 36:50.633
I'll get you another room.

36:55.840 --> 36:56.700
Miss,

36:56.700 --> 36:58.430
my master awaits downstairs.

37:32.220 --> 37:33.270
I truly apologize.

37:34.010 --> 37:34.870
My inn failed

37:34.870 --> 37:36.470
to care for you, Miss He.

37:36.950 --> 37:38.350
Sorry to startle you.

37:39.990 --> 37:40.950
Failed to care for me?

37:42.790 --> 37:43.640
From what I can see,

37:43.640 --> 37:44.620
you did quite well.

37:45.060 --> 37:45.910
You sent so many here

37:45.910 --> 37:47.020
to keep me company.

37:47.430 --> 37:48.700
What a surprise.

37:52.540 --> 37:54.100
You're traveling with spirit.

37:54.470 --> 37:55.310
How could they

37:55.620 --> 37:57.310
possibly harm you?

37:59.540 --> 38:00.380
Is that so?

38:02.390 --> 38:03.430
As I see it,

38:03.580 --> 38:04.430
what you mean is this:

38:05.350 --> 38:06.430
If they were to hurt me,

38:06.990 --> 38:07.870
they'd only kill

38:07.870 --> 38:09.020
a commoner at worst.

38:09.870 --> 38:11.350
You'd settle it with ease.

38:12.350 --> 38:13.870
But if they fail to hurt me,

38:14.580 --> 38:16.180
you can sound out my true depth.

38:26.470 --> 38:27.660
I overstepped.

38:28.700 --> 38:30.220
I beg your pardon.

38:35.790 --> 38:37.500
I'm simply very curious

38:38.870 --> 38:41.180
how you made this evil spirit

38:41.430 --> 38:42.390
obey you.

38:48.830 --> 38:49.990
Your spirit won't obey?

38:56.580 --> 38:57.580
I'd like to hear more.

39:04.500 --> 39:05.660
I was discourteous tonight.

39:06.390 --> 39:07.310
Tomorrow,

39:07.310 --> 39:09.180
I'll hold a garden party

39:09.180 --> 39:10.140
in my rear garden.

39:10.910 --> 39:12.380
I hope you'll honor us

39:12.620 --> 39:13.750
with your presence.

39:14.270 --> 39:15.310
I can be your friend.

39:16.990 --> 39:17.990
I do not make friends.

39:21.830 --> 39:22.790
But I can pay

39:23.220 --> 39:24.270
a visit to your garden.

39:58.540 --> 39:59.470
Lord of Jiling Temple,

40:00.620 --> 40:02.180
seeing you once

40:02.790 --> 40:03.910
has not been easy.

40:09.680 --> 40:15.010
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

40:15.340 --> 40:19.590
♪Light encountered shadow♪

40:20.950 --> 40:26.320
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

40:26.620 --> 40:31.220
♪The unbreakable fate♪

40:32.310 --> 40:34.150
♪Suddenly cracked♪

40:46.360 --> 40:51.800
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

40:51.980 --> 40:56.310
♪Light encountered shadow♪

40:57.680 --> 41:03.070
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

41:03.300 --> 41:07.240
♪The unbreakable fate♪

41:09.010 --> 41:10.900
♪Suddenly cracked♪

41:13.560 --> 41:16.720
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

41:16.720 --> 41:19.250
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

41:19.250 --> 41:24.770
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

41:24.770 --> 41:28.010
♪Following fate's guidance♪

41:28.010 --> 41:32.870
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

41:33.210 --> 41:36.230
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

41:36.230 --> 41:39.050
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

41:39.310 --> 41:41.840
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

41:41.840 --> 41:47.260
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

41:47.430 --> 41:50.500
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

41:50.660 --> 41:55.560
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

41:55.770 --> 41:59.240
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
